Vanaf versie 2.2.7 vanaf de huidige locatie.
version_message:
A probably last 2.2 update, moving some more things to sourcematching.
so we can some longer react to source changes.

32:
tvgids.tv has added several new channels to its repetour:
oorboekje.nl has merged the regional version for Radio 8fm and Joy Radio into one national listing.
31: Wild FM changed name to Wild Hitradio.
29:
HBO and Fox Life have closed.
Omroep Brabant is now 24/7 on Canal Digitaal, use 0-114.
28:
Nickelodeon and Spike changes, use the following:
         0-89: Nickelodeon 24/7.
        0-467: Spike 24/7.
1-nickelodeon: Combined Nickelodeon/Spike.
27:
Both Nieuwsblad.be and Primo.eu are renaming the Sundance Channel.
to Sundance TV. At present both the old and the new IDs work, but
in a few days the old IDs will stop working.
26:
tvgids.tv renamed the channelids for 'Q2', 'tV5 Monde', 'CAZ'  and 'NH'.
(rtv NoordHolland) and added a listing for 'Horse & Country TV'.
25: The this weekend starting Flemish channel Zes from SBS is now available as '8-zes'.
23: Q2 is a rename of 2BE, you can continue to use '0-59'.
22:
Both nieuwsblad.be and primo.eu now offer a listing for 'Q2'.
This Flemish successor of '2BE' is available with a chanid of '8-q2'.
21:
NPO.nl now has seperate listings for NPO Zapp Xtra and NPO Best, use the following:
     4-283: NPO Best only.
     4-288: NPO Zapp Xtra only.
1-zappelin: Combined NPO Zapp Xtra/NPO Best.
20:
vpro.nl now also has 'BBC First' and 'the History Channel'.
The ID on oorboekje.nl for 'radio NH' has changed to just 'nh'.
19: NPO Best and NPO Zapp Xtra are now one channel, use 1-zappelin
18: Food Network and Fine Living EMEA now available from tvgids.tv
16: Fox Sport 2, Fox Sport 3 and Fox Sport 4 now also on tvgids.nl
15: 13th Street, NPO Doc, NPO Humor TV and Syfy have ceased and several Horizon.tv IDs have changed.
14: BBC Three has shutdown completely, CBBC listing can now be found at 5-24443943013.
13:
Listings for standalone BBC Three (0-300) from tvgids.nl and vpro.nl have ceased.
BBC Three will shutdown completely on 11 April and CBBC will expand to 22:00, use the following:
          300: BBC Three stopt message.
5-24443943013: Combined BBC Three/CBBC.
      11-bbc3: Only BBC Three (20:00 - 6:30) - Will go away on 11 April.
      11-cbbc: Only CBBC (6:30 - 20:00) - Will expand to 22:00 on 11 April.
Private Spice (0-105) merged with Brazzers TV Europe (5-330522663235).
12: There is a new channellisting on NPO.nl for 'Elfstedentocht'.
11:
PrimeSport on Primo now merged with with Play Sports from Nieuwsblad.
London specific listings for BBC One now available from tvgids.tv.
VRT (10) now prime_source for VRT TV and Radio channels.
10:
Kadet (1-jim) on Humo moved from the old Jim-id '55' to '115'.
Now also with the right logo!.
Ons (0-406) is now also available from tvgids.tv.
8:
The Flemish channel Jim has stopped and is being replaced by Kadet.
We have maintained the chanid and xmltvid 1-jim for Kadet.
At present on Humo.be, Nieuwsblad.be and the new source Primo.eu.
7:
Horizon.tv (5) has changed the icon location and possibly iconnames.
The path is updated but to update the names run configure.
5:
For xmltvID 6-97 the sourceid for Nieuwsblad.be has changed from tmf
to it's replacement comedy-central (Flemish listing).
On Primo.eu it has changed to comedyscentral and on Humo to 113
4:
There is a new channel Spike (467) on tvgids.nl.
This channel shares with Nickelodeon. The new xmltvIDs are:
           89: Only Nickelodeon Netherlands.
         6-73: Only Nickelodeon Flanders.
          467: Only Spike (21:00 - 2:30.
  nickelodeon: Nickelodeon/Spike Netherlands.
8-nickelodeon: Nickelodeon/Spike Flanders.
2: TV5 Monde FBS has been split off from TV5 Monde Europe.
